node.text:
Happy Mother’s Day to all the wonderful moms out there 💕! My mom, @jenhill8 is my best friend and there is no one I can count on more. We had the best time reminiscing on our favorite memories together, sharing some of the best advice she’s given me over the years, and how we like to spend Mother’s Day together! 

Head over to the @RalphLaurenFragrances page to see a fun IG reels we did together too! 

#RalphLaurenRomance

•
